Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:33.02,Hackadoll_Ep_Title,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx90\fad(1,251)\pos(602.34,54.75)}Episódio 2: "Por Favor Nos Deixe Ser Idols!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:32.43,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,O que...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:34.49,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.99,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Triple booking? Não...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:39.20,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Fourth booking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:43.53,quadruple,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(318,303)}A frase correta é "quadruple booking."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:42.90,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,{\a6}Guess I screwed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:44.45,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Porém!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.04,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Resolver bagunças como essa is what makes a great producer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:50.29,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,O que são três ou quatro eventos? Eu consigo fill this schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.04,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,No, I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.60,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:55.29,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,I just can't fill this last slot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:58.18,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Se pelo menos houvesse uma agência que \Npudesse me apresentar pra uma idol livre...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.05,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,O que você precisa é...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:03.26,Hackadoll_Main,123,0,0,0,,A IA de Entretenimento Pessoal que sincroniza com você: HackaDoll!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.90,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,H-Hackadoll?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.81,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,The AI that can advance qualquer parte da vida de uma pessoa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.46,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Agora que estamos aqui, pode ficar tranquilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.56,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,We will be in the event that has an opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:16.03,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Huh? Vocês não iam me apresentar para uma idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.57,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Nós não precisamos fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:18.28,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Veja!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:20.04,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Veja o que podemos fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.67,Hackadoll_Main,2,0,0,0,,Aquilo não é CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:23.54,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Shiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.58,Hackadoll_Main,3,0,0,0,,Nós vamos ser idols?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:29.01,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,We'll wear cute costumes, cantar, dançar, \Nmake everyone go "squee!" for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.33,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,É o sonho de toda garota!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.34,Hackadoll_Main,2,0,0,0,,I think {\i1}you{\i0} just want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.34,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Eu aprecio a oferta, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.73,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:43.01,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,I promise we'll advance your company,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.60,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,então por favor, nos deixe ser idols!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.60,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,But I don't want to trouble the sponsor—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.85,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Please let us be idols!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.35,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Mas esse é um evento muito importan—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.35,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Nos deixe ser idols!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.61,Hackadoll_Main,2,0,0,0,,Só restam alguns dias antes do evento.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.14,Hackadoll_Main,2,0,0,0,,If you'd just give us a chance \Nand let us prove ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.35,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Yeah, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.27,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Let us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.99,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Está bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:07.48,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,We'll start you off com algumas lições.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.10,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:12.98,agency,1,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fscy50\frz18.43\frx16\fry340\pos(389,236)}Agên     cia de   Idols
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.73,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,We're ready to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.75,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0,0,0,,And so, our days of taking lessons began.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.53,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0,0,0,,Correndo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.05,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0,0,0,,Hopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.40,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0,0,0,,Hand-shaking practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.06,Hackadoll_Italics,3,0,0,0,,Sessões de fotos...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.26,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.82,hackadolls,Bold Text,0,0,0,,Ikebukuro Girls CD Shop                  {\b1}HackaDolls{\b0}                  Autograph Signing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:35.99,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,might just work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.43,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Finalmente chegou o grande dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.03,Hackadoll_Main,2,0,0,0,,É um público e tanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.07,Hackadoll_Main,3,0,0,0,,Eu estou nervosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.80,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,O evento de hoje é muito especial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.79,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Especial?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.30,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,É. O vencedor do evento de hoje
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:54.61,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,gets to release um CD de estreia from a major record label.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:58.71,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Ein?! E-Estreia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.93,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Só se vencerem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.80,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Ah, certo! Sem problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:08.39,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Já está quase na hora. Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.81,hackadolls2,1,0,0,0,,18:00~18:30         HackaDolls
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:14.81,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Banheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.24,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Now I'm really nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:22.43,Hackadoll_Main,Mob idol,0,0,0,,Você soube? There's a last-minute replacement today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:25.80,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 2,0,0,0,,Ah, está falando do grupo que afirma poder "progredir" as pessoas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.36,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 2,0,0,0,,{They're making a mockery of}Elas são uma piada como idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.24,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 3,0,0,0,,Elas não devem ter nada de especial.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.97,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 4,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't really get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:34.27,Hackadoll_Main,Mob 5,0,0,0,,I'm sure they won't get great results.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:39.11,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Mas nós trabalhamos muito duro pra isso! Eu sei que vamos conseguir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.67,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,But maybe the audience \Nwon't be satisfied with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.57,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Eu quero ser uma idol,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.73,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,mas se o público não ficar animado,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:51.31,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,então não posso progredir \Na carreira do produtor......
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:55.85,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,But I wonder if anyone will even watch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.00,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Meninas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.17,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,Produtor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.33,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Todas as idols enfrentam{struggle with} essa insegurança.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:09.69,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,And it's the miracle of overcoming \Nthat insecurity to stand no palco
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.62,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,que o público está aqui para ver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:17.33,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,I'm already excited to see what kind \Nof miracles you girls will perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:20.92,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Remember how badly you wanted to be an idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.34,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,And you want to advance my career, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.61,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:31.00,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que haverão \Npessoas assistindo vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:33.61,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,Now, go make miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:36.00,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.41,Hackadoll_Main,2,0,0,0,,Ainda estamos no banheiro das mulheres...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.33,Hackadoll_Main,Mob,0,0,0,,Quem são as próximas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.33,Hackadoll_Main,M,0,0,0,,Hackadolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:43.21,Hackadoll_Main,M,0,0,0,,Last-minute filler?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.29,Hackadoll_Main,M,0,0,0,,Eu conheço elas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.27,Hackadoll_Main,M,0,0,0,,São aquelas que podem "progredir" qualquer coisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.48,Hackadoll_Main,M,0,0,0,,Ah, aquelas lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.65,Hackadoll_Main,M,0,0,0,,Então elas podem ser idols também?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:49.95,Hackadoll_Main,M,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.20,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Prazer em conhecê-los! Nós somos as...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.95,Hackadoll_Main,123,0,0,0,,Hackadolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:59.00,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,We practiced lots to become idols today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.98,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Por favor, ouçam nossa música, "Cabbage Testing"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.51,cabbagesanction,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(235,435)}Cabbage Testing\N{\fs4.5}Letra: Ikuo Geso\NComposição: Daisuke Horita
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.58,Hackadoll_Main,Producer,0,0,0,,These vibrations...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.99,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,The building itself is resonating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:09.08,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Eu estraguei tudo, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.03,Hackadoll_Main,Otaku 1,0,0,0,,De maneira alguma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.83,Hackadoll_Main,Otaku 1,0,0,0,,#1-chan, you were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.45,Hackadoll_Main,Otaku 1,0,0,0,,Your soul reached me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:20.96,Hackadoll_Main,Otaku 1,0,0,0,,Foi o máximo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.71,Hackadoll_Main,1,0,0,0,,Muito obrigada!
